{
  "id": "RAW_27010832",
  "title": "重磅！今年最好的开源 9B/106B 视觉模型，出现了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwMzE4NjU5NA==&mid=2247512547&idx=1&sn=9c53e8852be525d0e608a8adf6958b21",
  "date": "2025-12-08 12:21:00",
  "author": "袋鼠帝AI客栈",
  "siteName": "袋鼠帝AI客栈",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b18dec40&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1DVSSxokfWUlgfvnqYnPqVR7fyjDxauP5YGoOxJtOawHyTe9EiaHaXYowYvnuz4qWrGRVMhucd8Bhw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwjv6sk1mi6\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大家好，我是袋鼠帝。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwjv6sk1069\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我发现智谱今年下半年是真滴猛。</span></p>\n  <p><span mpa-font-style=\"miwjv6sk217s\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">从7月份那个超强的10B视觉小模型GLM-4.1V-Thinking，再到后来的GLM-4.5V，以及10月</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">编程、Agent领域的GLM-4.6，</span><span leaf=\"\">每一款都打在了我的心巴上。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwjv6skmbs\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">本来以为到了年底，大家都在忙着做年终总结，没什么新东西了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwjv6sk1ctx\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没想到，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">智谱反手又卷起来了..</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100028848\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"240\" style=\"width: 148px;height: 148px;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=600b5aec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCWOliaFSfvwqH2icDf7ibSalicia8DSqtAq7FulJ0ibx29AZGUpRXAvQYPTwQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwjvopfji6\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">刚刚，智谱开源了他们最强的视觉模型：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">GLM-4.6V</span></span></p>\n  <p><span mpa-font-style=\"miwjvopf1akq\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">让我兴奋的是，这次一口气<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">开源了两个尺寸</span>：一个是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">106B的GLM-4.6V</span>，另一个是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">9B的GLM-4.6V-Flash</span>（</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">消费级显卡就能本地部署</span><span leaf=\"\">）。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwt53m7duo\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwt53n0y1u\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">在同参数量级下，多模态交互、逻辑推理、长上下文能力都取得了SOTA（State Of The Art，目前最强）。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwt5mna1h1n\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: normal;\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">太卷了，貌似现在不是SOTA都不好意思发布..</span></span></em></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwta0wp16of\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028895\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7296875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;background-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22c62056&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F3QzcPBL9P1DVSSxokfWUlgfvnqYnPqVRNOANuuIibW0KnYTtolZbL6DgIKWFHibS71uibicH5ibELEqiaW15Vdq8aIXw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrcw5l163u\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mivrcw691i8w\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">GLM-4.6V<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">支持128k上下文窗口</span>，可以一次性处理约150页PDF、200页PPT、近一小时的关键帧序列。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrihqf21nn\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mivrfw9xuky\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">不仅支持<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">多模态输入，还可以多模态输出</span>（图文并茂）</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrihqg1ipt\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了视觉能力强，还有<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">工具调用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">能力</span>，在z.ai集成了四种工具</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028885\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.43203125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=59537566&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCO4x7ia3DbfM29htyumaaYyQptyO6vC6vniaaTt0vbdoOI8GfIicLkrEHQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span mpa-font-style=\"miwiwe3295s\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwiwe3johx\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">一图胜千言（<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNjY0MzM1MA==&amp;mid=2247489013&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=e32cc86bbf5a18b1c0afda82add7f27f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"火柴人讲解万物 | Nano Banana Pro\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">提示词</a>来自朋友：@甲木，真好用）</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028894\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e39105a8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DVSSxokfWUlgfvnqYnPqVRXeuhjsUFmsAdzxRFluPauMz5bL9aYpy2EmXEibn0VL8y32iahBv5upqA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1bp2\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">体验下来，我的感觉是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">如果你想在本地玩视觉模型，这就是目前的版本答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizb9u\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">9B的GLM-4.6V-Flash</span>，意味着你不需要那种动辄几十万的专业GPU，哪怕是你家里的游戏本，或者是公司配的消费级显卡，都能随便跑起来。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwt6tpb1q24\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: normal;\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">整体表现超过Qwen3-VL-8B</span></span></em></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizb9u\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这对于很多注重数据隐私，或者需要在边缘设备上部署AI的企业来说，还是比较香的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizp2r\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我前段时间去杭州给一家国企做培训，参观了他们的生产车间。在那儿，我<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">看到了一个特别接地气的AI落地场景</span><span textstyle=\"\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizc6a\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">他们在产品流水线的末端，装了个摄像头和传感器。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz11yx\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">每当包装好的纸箱传送过来，摄像头就会咔嚓拍一张，然后传给旁边的一台普通电脑。电脑里跑着一个视觉模型，专门负责检查这个纸箱有没有破损，胶带封没封好。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwntvmlcr6\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: normal;\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">大概是下面这种场景（网图）</span></span></em></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028886\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f71b90b3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCEFCalP4XYiaWia0sLJBUfuqauYhkicO8Zj5kcYtDqGgvN84dr2RkpFStg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizxyo\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当时他们用的是阿里的一个小模型。我问了效果，负责人表示，虽然能用，但误判率还是不低。一些好好的箱子，也被AI判成了破损，导致工人还得去复核，挺折腾的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1e1p\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在就可以换成GLM-4.6V-Flash试试。同参数量下的SOTA，意味着在同样的硬件条件下，它的性能会更好，准确度也会提升。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz11c3\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">106B的GLM-4.6V</span>，说大不大，说小也不小。它不像DeepSeek R1那种671B的巨无霸，除了大厂，没几个企业能私有化部署得起。106B，属于那种努努力，够一够，还是能玩得起的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizwe3\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如果你对性能有要求，又必须把数据掌握在自己手里，那这个106B的版本，是一个现阶段完美的平衡点。</span></p>\n  <p data-mpa-action-id=\"miwzhjgf1l0s\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwzhjfr1itr\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上次我在成都遇到OneOneTalk的彭总，他就在用一台2万多的华硕本，本地跑了一个120B的开<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">源模型：</span></span><strong node=\"[object Object]\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"miwzhjfr12u2\"><span leaf=\"\">gpt‑oss‑120b</span></span></strong></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwnucqoseg\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: normal;\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">就是下面这台性能猛兽</span></span></em></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028852\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 346px;height: 260px;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=03a005b9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQC8nIU113lb1eiaiafdXMHdUftN8iczdwDlziboFOuQW1PNEf8SS2U689nsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizs9r\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，如果你不在乎数据上云，直接调智谱的API，速度和体验会更好。</span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrjmg5kgp\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">目前GLM-4.6V可以在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">z.ai</span>上使用，也能<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">以MCP的形式接入Agent</span>使用（做本地Agent的眼睛👀）</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrjmg5v6b\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">还能<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">接入Claude Code当作基模</span>使用。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrln14dl8\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我接入Claude Code之后，让它执行了复杂的多平台价格对比，条件筛选商品的任务。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrln14k3r\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">完成得很好：</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwnwjjh1dwa\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwnwjjx12a4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">GLM-4.6V<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">开源地址汇总</span>，方便大家直达：</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mivru9qqfxs\">\n   <div style=\"width: 100%;padding: 0 10px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <p style=\"width: 14px;height: 13px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;z-index: 1;margin: 0 0 -9px -1px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"background-color: transparent;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9285714285714286\" data-w=\"28\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5562ef56&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FibelX39p4gkmLa6XvTYIqqXo0ziaBUEFXt6gpmMOOQJnPSLVU6auGI4jJ52z9nUMlQRkUu593LtIhAkvAx9eEuhA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;align-self: flex-start;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"width: 100%;display: flex;align-items: flex-start;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"width: 11px;height: 6px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;flex-shrink: 0;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"background-color: transparent;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5833333333333334\" data-w=\"24\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ad5d998b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlIQ87GZ2CQudhDaMADia7Lk87uAC193q9riboribMBrmnKEfazIPNmGyybp654xwjTYQINQedT3fIlCu45qweaWLw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"padding:7px 10px 11px 11px;width:100%;text-align:center;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <div style=\"width: 100%;text-align: left;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">GitHub：</span></p>\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-V\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/zai-org/GLM-V</a></span></p>\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugging Face：</span></p>\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/collections/zai-org/glm-46v\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/collections/zai-org/glm-46v</a></span></p>\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">魔搭社区：</span></p>\n        <p yb-mpa-mark=\"mark-style-text\" style=\"word-break:break-word;font-size:14px;line-height:26px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://modelscope.cn/collections/GLM-46V-37fabc27818446\" target=\"_blank\">https://modelscope.cn/collections/GLM-46V-37fabc27818446</a></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"width: 14px;height: 13px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;margin: -10px -4px 0 0;align-self: flex-end;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"background-color: transparent;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9285714285714286\" data-w=\"28\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0f3d0555&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FdbY9cVHpfI1Ft4Cox8GXOurG1u3BbjHrvLZJYCA9hQYwWd5V7icB79Y6yVR1XoJPyRKhqp3HjPp5iaqicKswDHlXQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz14nb\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我也第一时间在z.ai上，测试了GLM-4.6V：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz866\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">之前一直有个难题，就是在那种<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">大合照里，识别出某个人的位置</span>。我试过很多模型，甚至包括Gemini 3，效果都不咋地。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028849\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5537037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f7d70670&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCibl4tIR5jNiaVD70CSSOxOiahTLwfFdeCNWsCTOZSSwiaUZJmsW7AlphTg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizfbd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我明明在第一排，从左往右数的第三个。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz251c\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我同样把上次昆明Trae活动的大合照，加上一张我的自拍照，一起扔给了GLM-4.6V。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100028850\" data-ratio=\"0.43333333333333335\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8000eae8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCh0LlCvGe6ow5oNpS87XibCglynibd56oz5k1eIdRgzXkjic6ibO3MazhZQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz13bf\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果，</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">GLM-4.6V</span><span leaf=\"\">居然准确的找到了我！这还让我蛮惊讶的。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizhb7\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这对于以后做智能相册管理，或者安防监控领域来说，太有用了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz9a7\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">z.ai里面还有一个<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Image Research</span>功能，对我来说挺实用的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz11gy\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我写公众号的时候，经常需要找各种配图、或者封面图。以前我都是去Google各种搜图，有时候搜出来的图很多都不是我想要的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz11qe\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这次我让它帮我搜几张关于GEO（Generative Engine Optimization）生成式引擎优化的图片。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028851\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5370370370370371\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ff2ef034&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCO4rvCWeES5zBibUHbooNFUYoyn7v3icpdE9Q4UJOQqHic8RvdzjyOtCkQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizxpq\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它搜出来的图，非常精准，质量高。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz14as\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其中一张，正好就是我上一篇GEO的文章用到的封面图。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwnziouyw\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: normal;\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">以后我的封面图工作流又要升级了（增加一个环节）。</span></span></em></p>\n   <p><em><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;用NanoBanana Pro生成创意图的同时，用GLM-4.6V搜图，最后我只负责选。</span></span></em></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizjex\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说到搜图，这次的GLM-4.6V还能直接<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">产出图文并茂的文章</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1w0i\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这得益于它的工具调用能力</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizmc6\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如我让它生成北京旅游的推文</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz6dr\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">解读GEO的PDF论文（论文PDF中的图片也会被它插入到正确的位置）</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028857\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"3.5027777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 335px;height: 1173px;border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5bc6ffb7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCHaqUbez4lE3oFUo4sYDYPtvAd9mXyXA7KWHicnia0aQvZUic8vUcGzH1g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz174q\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上次不是写了一篇飞书多维表格的教程嘛，在评论区看到，还是有一些朋友不清楚怎么调用的NanoBanana Pro API</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1qt4\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我给大家演示一下， 你只需要把不懂的部分截图，丢给GLM-4.6V，它就能帮你把散落在5张图的API请求，按照想要的形式组装起来了。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mivl1y08e09\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-mpa-template-id=\"771\" data-mpa-category=\"模板\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div data-mpa-category=\"模板\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"width: 100%;display: grid;grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;grid-column-gap: 7px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028861\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4444444444444444\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74ea8721&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCmB2eDuLiaoQCmfbQMYyDFwYohor0bSm05Uy2zRX4S41bU7MnrFneQ5g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028858\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.238888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7f373332&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmb