-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bb75000c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCiakUR5Qs5ogILYaNpbIDEy6XIUueJEUwkj4JW2zPphrLd5FCuXkEJwg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwo3qa514hf\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: normal;\"><em><span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-is-content=\"t\"><span leaf=\"\">有高手能评论区教一下怎么才能停成这样吗？？我每次离别人车还有30cm就不敢继续靠近了..</span></span></em></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz9c5\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了黑车品牌没有猜对，其他都对了，挺强的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1gqc\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">上次车停在车位被剐蹭了，去调监控，花了几个小时终于把逃逸者找到了..</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizy0l\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我把最后的<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">维修单丢给GLM-4.6V识别</span></span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mivmttguywz\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-mpa-template-id=\"771\" data-mpa-category=\"模板\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div data-mpa-category=\"模板\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"width: 100%;display: grid;grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;grid-column-gap: 7px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100028864\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=63274ee7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCcnXdBpT2tCAEiaLOy6Gkt50d4XmslYTOOclkzp8JBK3lGpGbqVHnX3w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028865\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.67578125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78342de5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQC68EzcFDl1vf3P8pQQRgdtT6HAHxqMO9qQI1GsJ6Sggib7ciba7OLR3oQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz245w\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">经过我的逐字检查，准确率非常高，大概是99.9%</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz14sr\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它还<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">能识别影帝的情绪～</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz19gb\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">渣渣辉封神片段：你知道我这五年怎么过的吗？</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100028893\" data-ratio=\"1.011111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1385a8b0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1DVSSxokfWUlgfvnqYnPqVRicvcFre4x0CAGeS2bUHliacSoSUB2GOeBmkp3fjtDk4ctL7dLibBmtUiaA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1a8y\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">剧情、情绪的变化都识别的相当nice。而且非常细节，角色湿润的眼眶都识别到了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1xuj\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除了在z.ai使用，GLM-4.6V还可以接入Claude Code</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1qcr\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也可以把GLM-4.6V通过MCP的方式，接入Claude Code。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1p3z\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">接入Claude Code</span>，可以参考官方文档：</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizc2l\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/develop/claude\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.bigmodel.cn/cn/guide/develop/claude</a></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1awd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">或者直接修改Claude的settings.json配置文件：</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"json\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">{</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"env\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">{</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"你的智谱开放平台apikey\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">,</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"<a href=\"https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/anthropic\" target=\"_blank\">https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/anthropic</a>\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">,</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"API_TIMEOUT_MS\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"3000000\"</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">},</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">\"model\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">:</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"glm-4.6v\"</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">}</span></span></code><br></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrah8ioic\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">配置好之后，重启Claude，你就拥有了一个有手有眼的本地Agent啦～</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrah8ic1a\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">既然有手有眼了，那就让它干点实事儿。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrah8ifta\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我给这个本地Agent<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">布置了一个较复杂的任务：</span>使用playwright MCP，通过浏览器查找，进行产品的全网比价，提示词如下：</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mivnkq8i1ok8\">\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima, 'Microsoft YaHei', PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"></p>\n   <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 4px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\">Prompt：全程使用playwright MCP工具。先在淘宝上找一款半入耳式蓝牙耳机，价格在500-1000元之间。找到销量第一的那款。然后，拿着这款耳机的型号，去唯品会和京东比价，找到最便宜的那个平台，并把它加到我的购物车里。</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz2ox\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个任务，涉及到了多平台的网页浏览、视觉识别（看价格、看型号）、逻辑判断（比大小）和操作执行，对于现阶段的所有视觉大模型来说，都是一个挑战。</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwo5ekife3\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GLM-4.6V负责看网页信息，Claude Code负责任务的调度。两者配合，居然真的把这个复杂的流程给跑通了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwo5ekivpp\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">美中不足的是漏掉了筛选价格区间的操作，但其余的任务几乎完美实现。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwo5eki1dkr\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在淘宝找销量第一的半入耳式蓝牙耳机，以及跟唯品会、京东同款耳机比价，最后把价格最划算的商品都加入了购物车</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mivnwbfd1vq1\">\n   <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" data-mpa-template-id=\"771\" data-mpa-category=\"模板\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n    <div data-mpa-category=\"模板\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n     <div style=\"width: 100%;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n      <div style=\"width: 100%;display: grid;grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;grid-column-gap: 7px;\" data-mid=\"\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100028875\" data-ratio=\"0.24296875\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f5f822cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCFkXawxA5ZwrnGL7BCp3YB6emg29XxZQoC7A7YZKdxib4DsTriaQ4ibGHg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-img-disable-preview=\"f\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100028876\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4328125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"border-radius: 6px;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: transparent;box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;pointer-events: auto;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4db61350&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F3QzcPBL9P1D0KDyKibX8F4IwJibxJJqSQCicEncbLl35IlvmO1rxEGfAibmaMYxnPGJCxpP6rNq9HTnfltm3o57lAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivphpzwtei\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我觉得虽然GLM-4.6V可以写代码，但是它的代码能力还是会比GLM-4.6差一些</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivphpzwqk0\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我决定<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">让它在Claude Code里面做GLM-4.6的眼睛</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivphpzwqk0\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也就是作为MCP-Server使用</span></p>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">claude</span>&nbsp;mcp add -s user zai-mcp-server --env Z_AI_API_KEY=你的智谱apikey -- npx -y&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"</span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\"><span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">@z_ai</span></span><span class=\"code-snippet__string\">/mcp-server\"</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz246h\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在settings.json里面把模型换回glm-4.6即可</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz246h\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">既然有了眼睛，那复刻网页就不用我费劲去描述了。</span></p>\n  <div data-mpa-template=\"t\" mpa-data-temp-power-by=\"yiban.io\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwo61uf1i5c\">\n   <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima, 'Microsoft YaHei', PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-from-tpl=\"t\"></p>\n   <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 4px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-is-content=\"t\">Prompt：使用zai-mcp-server分析当前目录下的视频，分析视频中的网站的页面、交互、动效，然后1:1复刻视频中的网站</span></code></pre>\n   <p></p>\n  </div>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizlya\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">原网站效果</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizlya\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">复刻后的效果</span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiziix\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GLM-4.6V负责识别视频，GLM-4.6负责生成高质量的前端代码。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwzuvrv1lk2\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwzuvsg11eg\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">网页复刻得还不错，至少这个卡片飞来飞去的效果有了，整体交互和动效都有原视频的影子。要想一次性百分百还原是很难的，毕竟原视频的动效太棒了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizeno\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GLM-4.6V虽然在极致的视觉能力上，它可能还略逊于Gemini 3这种顶级模型。但别忘了，它只有106B。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizkhh\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对于想要私有化部署的企业来说，这是一个够一够就能得着的高性价比选项。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizxw0\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而对于个人开发者，9B的Flash版本够我们在本地免费使用了。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1z8b\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过，我心里也有个小疑问：为什么智谱不直接把视觉能力融合进GLM-4.6里，要分拆成两个模型呢？有没有懂的朋友在评论区给我科普一下？</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqiz1z8b\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我猜可能是为了更灵活的部署和更低的推理成本？</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivniqizas\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">顺便说一下，行业+AI，才能真正释放AI的生产力。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwo6xj3ma1\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">懂业务的朋友，真的建议多学学怎么用好这些AI模型。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwo6xj3f8m\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当你能把业务痛点和模型能力对接上的那一刻，效率的提升，绝对是指数级的。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"miwo6xj318c8\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">补充：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">GLM-4.6和GLM-4.6V都在Coding Plan的使用范围内</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mfjqnp98moe\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrxe2w36y\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\">能看到这里的都是凤毛麟角的存在！</span></span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrxe2wp1w\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧~</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrxe2wgcq\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mf0wuuj414kl\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 17px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mivrxe2w191x\">谢谢你耐心看完我的文章~</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "智谱发布了两款开源视觉大模型 GLM-4.6V（106B）和 GLM-4.6V-Flash（9B），在多模态交互、逻辑推理、长上下文能力上达到 SOTA，并详细测评了其在本地部署、图像识别、Agents 集成等场景下的卓越表现。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "智谱发布了两款开源视觉大模型 GLM-4.6V（106B）和 GLM-4.6V-Flash（9B），在多模态交互、逻辑推理、长上下文能力上达到 SOTA，并详细测评了其在本地部署、图像识别、Agents 集成等场景下的卓越表现。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了智谱最新开源的视觉大模型 GLM-4.6V 系列，包括 106B 和 9B 两个版本。作者通过大量实测，展示了其在图像识别、多模态输出、工具调用以及 Agent 集成方面的强大能力。9B 版本 GLM-4.6V-Flash 可在消费级显卡上本地部署，解决了数据隐私和边缘部署问题，并在工业质检场景中展示出巨大潜力。106B 版本则在性能和私有化部署之间取得了平衡。文章还通过实战案例，如人脸识别、图片搜索、商品比价和网页复刻等，生动地说明了 GLM-4.6V 如何作为 Agent 的“眼睛”，与 GLM-4.6 等模型协同工作，大幅提升复杂任务的处理效率和用户体验。文章也对模型的开源地址和接入方法进行了详细说明。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "智谱开源 GLM-4.6V 系列视觉模型，提供 106B 和 9B 两种规模选择。",
      "explanation": "GLM-4.6V 在同参数量级下，多模态交互、逻辑推理、长上下文能力达到 SOTA，为不同硬件条件的开发者和企业提供灵活选择。"
    },
    {
      "point": "9B 的 GLM-4.6V-Flash 可在消费级显卡上本地部署，降低了 AI 落地门槛。",
      "explanation": "该版本解决了数据隐私和边缘部署难题，尤其适用于工业质检等对本地算力有需求的场景，性能超越同级别竞争对手。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GLM-4.6V 具备强大的多模态输入/输出与工具调用能力。",
      "explanation": "支持 128k 上下文窗口，可处理大量文档和视频关键帧，并实现图文并茂的输出，结合工具调用能力能执行复杂任务。"
    },
    {
      "point": "GLM-4.6V 可作为 Agent 的“眼睛”，与 Claude Code 等 Agent 框架深度集成。",
      "explanation": "通过接入 Agent，GLM-4.6V 能赋能 Agent 进行复杂的视觉识别和理解任务，如全网比价、网页复刻，大幅提升自动化能力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "GLM-4.6V，今年本地 Agent 最后的视觉救星来了，附一手实测",
    "让我兴奋的是，这次一口气开源了两个尺寸：一个是 106B 的 GLM-4.6V，另一个是 9B 的 GLM-4.6V-Flash（消费级显卡就能本地部署）。",
    "体验下来，我的感觉是：如果你想在本地玩视觉模型，这就是目前的版本答案。",
    "不过，我心里也有个小疑问：为什么智谱不直接把视觉能力融合进 GLM-4.6 里，要分拆成两个模型呢？有没有懂的朋友在评论区给我科普一下？",
    "行业+AI，才能真正释放 AI 的生产力。当你能把业务痛点和模型能力对接上的那一刻，效率的提升，绝对是指数级的。"
